data.description: This is a very well kept up home. This property is located in Stockdale Ranch Villas Community. Nice neighborhood that belongs to Rosedale union school District and Kern High School district. Property has 3 Bedrooms + 2 Bathrooms! Enjoy the large back yard and covered patio for Summer BBQ's and space to add spa/pool. The Kitchen has a breakfast bar that provides a view to the living room. The primary bedroom is perfectly placed separated from the other 2 bedrooms with its own attached bathroom with dual sinks, shower tub combination for added convenience. No HOA, No Mello roos and minutes away from shopping plazas and restaurants.
